Audible Tic Tac Toe Game

You can use your voice to command this game.
For example say: How to play
We need Record Audio Permission to listen your voice command.

The Audible Tic Tac Toe game lets you control the game with spoken commands. Use your voice to navigate between screens, quit the game, and make moves in the game. 
Just say the button name using your voice.

For example: Start Game 
On the game screen, it is enough to say the numbers in the game area. After the saying number, the player's mark will be added to the game area.

For example: Eight
To return to the previous screen just say: Back
